===== mental disorder or magic spell =====
A more extreme example of mental disorder might produce a counter example.
Suppose I am somehow compelled to believe something, for instance, that I will
die I step outside my house. Suppose that I have mental disorder which compels
me to hold this belief. I might be aware of this, I have read the medical
reports, seen the scan of the very particular brain lesion, understand that my
belief is merely caused by this brain damage, and yet still be unable to shake
it.
